Package: starsExtra
Title: Miscellaneous functions for working with 'stars' rasters
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Dorman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dorman@post.bgu.ac.il")
Description: Miscellaneous functions for working with 'stars' objects, mainly single-band rasters. Currently includes functions for: (1) extracting raster values as vector or as matrix, (2) applying focal filter.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    stars
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
